<Data CreatedBy="admin" CreatedOn="634110058660339020" UpdatedBy="admin" UpdatedOn="634118008973820567">
  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Change selected item of 'TextAlign' <em>ComboBox </em>and the <em>TextAlign </em>property&nbsp;of&nbsp;<em>CheckBox&nbsp;</em>value will be change. Change selected item of 'CheckAlign' <em>ComboBox </em>and&nbsp;the <em>CheckAlign </em>property of <em>CheckBox&nbsp;</em>value&nbsp; will be change</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>CheckBox </em>control contains <em>CheckAlign </em>and <em>TextAlign </em>properties. The <em>CheckAlign </em>defines the check box alignment on the <em>CheckBox </em>control. The <em>TextAlign </em>defines the text alignment on the <em>CheckBox</em> control. These properties can be contains the following values:<br /><strong>TopLeft </strong>&ndash; check box/text/check box is vertically aligned at the top, and horizontally aligned on the left;<br /><strong>TopCenter </strong>- check box/text is vertically aligned at the top, and horizontally aligned at the center;<br /><strong>TopRight </strong>- check box/text is vertically aligned at the top, and horizontally aligned on the right;<br /><strong>MiddleLeft </strong>- check box/text is vertically aligned in the middle, and horizontally aligned on the left;<br /><strong>MiddleCenter </strong>- check box/text is vertically aligned in the middle, and horizontally aligned at the center;<br /><strong>MiddleRight </strong>- check box/text is vertically aligned in the middle, and horizontally aligned on the right;<br /><strong>BottomLeft </strong>- check box/text is vertically aligned at the bottom, and horizontally aligned on the left;<br /><strong>BottomCenter </strong>- check box/text is vertically aligned at the bottom, and horizontally aligned at the center;<br /><strong>BottomRight </strong>- check box/text  is vertically aligned at the bottom, and horizontally aligned on the right.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
